name: Eye of Providence
description:
The Eye of Providence (or the All-Seeing Eye) watching over you, accented by the cosmic influence to energise your spiritual growth. All-Seeing Eye is a symbol showing an eye enclosed in a triangle and surrounded by rays of lights or a glory. 
A well known example of the Eye of Providence appears on the reverse of the Great Seal of the United States, which is depicted on the United States one-dollar bill.
It is the my first NFT to be minted that uses the ZIM JavaScript Canvas Framework at https://zimjs.com. Inspired and forked by "Eye of the Dragon" https://dev.to/zimlearn/eye-of-the-dragon-10li buy DrAbstract.
